file.name: parameters.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Parameter Component
  version: 1.0.0

paths: {}

components:
  parameters:
    # path
    node_id_required:
      name: node_id
      in: path
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    bucket_id_required:
      name: bucket_id
      in: path
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    channel_id_required:
      name: channel_id
      in: path
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    group_id_required:
      name: group_id
      in: path
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
        format: uuid
    resource_owner_id_required:
      name: resource_owner_id
      in: path
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    object_id_required:
      name: object_id
      in: path
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    session_id_required:
      name: session_id
      in: path
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    device_id:
      name: device_id
      in: path

      schema:
        type: string
    client_id:
      name: client_id
      in: path
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    device_id_required:
      name: device_id
      in: path
      description: デバイスID
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    point_id_required:
      name: point_id
      in: path
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    circle_id_required:
      name: circle_id
      in: path
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    route_id_required:
      name: route_id
      in: path
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    video_id:
      name: video_id
      in: path
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    policy_id:
      name: policy_id
      in: path
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    name:
      name: name
      in: path
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    key:
      name: key
      in: path
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    component:
      name: component
      in: path
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    lifecycle_id:
      name: lifecycle_id
      in: path
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    contract_id:
      name: contract_id
      in: path
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    user_id_path:
      name: user_id
      in: path
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    collection_id:
      description: コレクション名
      explode: false
      in: path
      name: collection_id
      required: true
      schema:
        description: コレクション名
        example: location
        pattern: ^[a-zA-Z0-9][a-zA-Z0-9-_]{1,34}[a-zA-Z0-9]$
        title: CollectionId
        type: string
      style: simple
    series_id:
      description: シリーズID
      explode: false
      in: path
      name: series_id
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    timestamp_path:
      description: UNIXタイム(ミリ秒)
      explode: false
      in: path
      name: timestamp
      required: true
      schema:
        description: UNIXタイム(ミリ秒)
        example: 1518165596566320
        format: int64
        title: TimeStamp
        type: integer
      style: simple


    # query
    resource_owner_id_query_required:
      name: resource_owner_id
      in: query
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    name_query:
      name: name
      description: 名前での部分一致検索
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        pattern: \A.{1,100}\z
        type: string
        maxLength: 255
    key_query:
      name: key
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    serial_number_query:
      name: serial_number
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    node_id_query:
      name: node_id
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    session_id_query:
      name: session_id
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    parent_node_id:
      name: parent_node_id
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    parent_key:
      name: parent_key
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    group_id:
      name: group_id
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    user_id:
      name: user_id
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
        format: uuid
    type:
      name: type
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    group_type:
      name: type
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
        enum: [ Corporation, Group ]
    device_id_query:
      name: device_id
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    is_enable:
      name: is_enable
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    page:
      name: page
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    offset:
      name: offset
      in: query
      required: false
      description: ページネーションのうち、何件読み飛ばすか
      schema:
        type: integer
        description: 0以上
        minimum: 0
        format: int64
    limit:
      name: limit
      in: query
      required: false
      description: ページネーションのうち、上位何件取得するか
      schema:
        type: integer
        format: int64
        minimum: 1
        maximum: 1000
    group_order_by:
      name: order_by
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
        enum: [ display_name ]
    member_order_by:
      name: order_by
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
        enum: [ role, category ]
    node_order_by:
      name: order_by
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
        enum: [ parent_node_id, name, key, created_at, updated_at, file_size ]
    order_by:
      name: order_by
      description: ソート対象。指定順に高優先でのソートとなる
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    order:
      name: order
      description: ソート順序。 order_byで指定したkeyそれぞれに対して昇順、降順を配列で指定
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
        enum: [ desc, asc ]
    recursive:
      name: recursive
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: boolean
    is_directory:
      name: is_directory
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: boolean
    directory_size:
      name: directory_size
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: boolean
    force:
      name: force
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: boolean
    checksum:
      name: checksum
      in: query
      required: true
      schema:
        type: string
    lang:
      description: 言語指定
      name: lang
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        description: |-
          IETF言語タグ(BCP47)準拠。
          指定言語が設定されていない場合デフォルト言語(display_info.is_defaultがtrueの言語)を利用する
        type: string
    is_dev:
      name: is_dev
      in: query
      required: false
      description: 開発者モードの有効・無効
      schema:
        type: boolean
        description: |-
          true:display_infoを表示,
          false:langで指定した言語のnameとdescriptionを表示
    is_public:
      name: is_public
      in: query
      description: デバイスの公開・非公開
      required: false
      schema:
        description: |-
          true:公開されているものでの絞り込み,
          false:所有するものでの絞り込み,
          all:絞り込みなし
        type: string
        enum: [true, false, all]
    messaging_enabled:
      name: messaging_enabled
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    datastore_enabled:
      name: datastore_enabled
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    messaging_persisted:
      name: messaging_persisted
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    channel_protocol:
      name: channel_protocol
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    channel_protocol_id:
      name: channel_protocol_id
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    channel_protocol_version:
      name: channel_protocol_version
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: integer
    location:
      name: location
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    ascending:
      name: ascending
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: boolean
    location_range:
      name: location_range
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    timestamp_range:
      name: timestamp_range
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    timestamp:
      name: timestamp
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    resource_owner_id:
      name: resource_owner_id
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
        format: uuid
    label:
      name: label
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    state:
      name: state
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    city:
      name: city
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    address_1:
      name: address_1
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    address_2:
      name: address_2
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    tag:
      name: tag
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    tags:
      name: tags
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    domain:
      name: domain
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    parent_group_id:
      name: parent_group_id
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
        format: uuid
    includes:
      name: includes
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    category:
      name: category
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
        enum: [ member, guest ]
    role:
      name: role
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
        enum: [ super_admin, admin, manager, staff ]
    phonetic_given_name:
      name: phonetic_given_name
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    phonetic_family_name:
      name: phonetic_family_name
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    primary:
      name: primary
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: boolean
    email:
      name: email
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    packer_format:
      name: packer_format
      required: false
      in: query
      schema:
        type: string
    channel_id_query_required:
      name: channel_id
      required: true
      in: query
      schema:
        type: string
    definition_id:
      name: definition_id
      description: |-
        デバイス定義ID(custom_inventory.definition_id)での完全一致検索
      required: false
      in: query
      schema:
        type: string
    id_number:
      name: id_number
      required: false
      description: 識別番号での完全一致検索
      in: query
      schema:
        type: string
    definition_tag:
      name: definition_tag
      description: デバイス定義のタグ(custom_inventory.tag)での完全一致検索
      required: false
      in: query
      schema:
        type: string
    inventory_key:
      name: definition_tag
      description: |-
        custominventoryの内部データでの検索時に指定。
        key,valueのセットの完全一致での検索とし、
        本パラメータでkeyを指定し、inventory_valueでvalueを指定する。
      required: false
      in: query
      schema:
        type: string
    inventory_value:
      name: definition_tag
      description: |-
        custominventoryの内部データでの検索時に指定。
        key,valueのセットの完全一致での検索とし、本パラメータでvalueを指定し、
        inventory_keyでkeyを指定する。
      required: false
      in: query
      schema:
        type: string
    sort:
      name: sort
      required: false
      in: query
      schema:
        type: string
    top:
      name: top
      required: false
      in: query
      schema:
        type: integer
    skip:
      name: skip
      required: false
      in: query
      schema:
        type: integer
    version:
      name: version
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    component_key:
      name: component_key
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    component_value:
      name: component_value
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    component_id_query:
      name: component_id_query
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    is_flat:
      name: is_flat
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: boolean
        default: false
    is_recursive:
      name: is_recursive
      in: query
      required: true
      schema:
        type: boolean
    event_kind:
      name: event_kind
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    event_mode:
      name: event_mode
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    event_type:
      name: event_type
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    component_id:
      name: component_id
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    before_id:
      name: before_id
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    after_id:
      name: after_id
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    start_event_at:
      name: start_event_at
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    end_event_at:
      name: end_event_at
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    maker_id:
      name: end_event_at
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    status:
      name: status
      in: query
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
    is_latest:
      description: 最新画像としてアップロードする場合はtrue。保存に失敗した画像を再度アップロードする場合など、最新画像でない場合はfalseを指定する。
      explode: true
      in: query
      name: is_latest
      required: false
      schema:
        default: true
        example: false
        type: boolean
      style: form
    time_range:
      description: <開始時刻>:<終了時刻>、UNIX時間(ミリ秒)。開始時刻はInclusive、終了時刻はExclusive(開始時刻≦取得範囲＜終了時刻)。最大で取得できる期間は7日間以内とする。開始、終了時刻の指定が7日間を超える場合は、400エラーとなる
      explode: true
      in: query
      name: time_range
      required: true
      schema:
        example: 1518165596566:1518165596566
        pattern: ^((0)|([1-9][0-9]*)):((0)|([1-9][0-9]*))$
        type: string
      style: form
    projection:
      description: |-
        取得する対象を以下から選択する

        |値|取得対象|
        |---|---|
        |data|画像以外の最新データのみ取得。時系列データ保存APIで保存された各シリーズの時系列データで最後に保存されたデータが返却される。時系列データ保存 (bulk upload)で保存されたデータは取得されない。|
        |thumbnail|最新のサムネイル画像のみ取得。画像保存APIで各シリーズに対してis_latest=trueを指定して最後に保存された画像が返却される。|
        |image|最新のオリジナル画像のみ取得。画像保存APIで各シリーズに対してis_latest=trueを指定して最後に保存された画像が返却される。|
      explode: true
      in: query
      name: projection
      required: false
      schema:
        default: data
        enum: [ data, thumbnail, image ]
        type: string
      style: form
    month_required:
      description: 問い合わせ年月(YYYY-MM)。1970-01から9999-12まで
      example: 2019-12
      explode: true
      in: query
      name: month
      required: true
      schema:
        pattern: ^[0-9]{4}-(0[1-9]|1[0-2])$
        type: string
      style: form
    gmt_offset:
      description: タイムゾーンをGMTからのオフセットで指定(日本の場合9) hh:mmの形式で指定。時間が一桁の場合は0パディングはなし。時間は[-12, 14]の範囲。分は、00, 15, 30, 45のいずれかのみ許容
      explode: true
      in: query
      name: gmt_offset
      required: false
      schema:
        default: 0:00
        pattern: ^(0|-?[1-9]|-1[0-1]|1[0-3]):(00|15|30|45)$|^(-12:00|14:00)$
        type: string
      style: form
    interval:
      description: 時系列データを集計する単位時間（ミリ秒）を指定する
      explode: true
      in: query
      name: interval
      required: true
      schema:
        example: 60000
        format: int32
        maximum: 86400000
        minimum: 1000
        type: integer
      style: form
    # header
    Accept-Encoding:
      description: レスポンスボディの圧縮形式。gzipのみ対応。
      explode: false
      in: header
      name: Accept-Encoding
      required: false
      schema:
        pattern: gzip
        type: string
      style: simple
